The paper deals with signal processing and optimization techniques for blind deconvolution, which are common topics in the Information Theory (cs.IT), Signal Processing (cs.SP), and Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. The use of convex programs is also a key aspect of the paper, which is a popular optimization technique in Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Scientific Computing (cs.SI).
